    "question": "British painter Peter Edwards has a ______ painting portraits of notable figures from a variety of different fields. These characteristic works include his esteemed portraits of poet Wendy Cope and soccer player and coach Ryan Griggs. Which choice completes the text with the most logical and precise word or phrase?",
