    "skill": "Words in Context",
    "difficulty": "Medium",
    "passage": "The Illustrated History of San Mateo County, published in 1878, features several illustrations by Grafton Tyler Brown showing the California county’s farms, residences, and businesses. It was ______ for a business to be featured, since being included suggested that a business was an important part of the community.",
